6
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:52,520
This is your retribution.

7
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:54,880
Your mother set up my mother

8
00:00:55,390 --> 00:00:57,520
and made her die of depression
in the deserted palace.

9
00:00:58,070 --> 00:00:59,200
I had to grow up alone

10
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,710
