11
00:01:01,070 --> 00:01:02,470
in the deserted palace.

12
00:01:07,350 --> 00:01:08,560
You deserve this.

13
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:10,150
It's all your fault.

14
00:01:10,790 --> 00:01:11,920
You and your mother owe me,

15
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:12,790
understand?

16
00:01:13,510 --> 00:01:14,920
If you beg me,

17
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:17,000
maybe I'll have mercy

18
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:18,590
and spare your life.

19
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:24,000
I'll never surrender to a rebel.

20
00:01:25,350 --> 00:01:27,280
I'm the winner!

21
00:01:27,310 --> 00:01:28,150
It's me!

22
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:32,760
In the end,

23
00:01:33,070 --> 00:01:34,560
